snippet.title: AaaaaAAaaaAAAaaAAAAaAAAAA!!! for the Awesome
snippet.description:
AaaaaAAaaaAAAaaAAAAaAAAAA!!! for the Awesome is the semi-sequel to our award-winning 2009 BASE jumping title, AaaaaAAaaaAAAaaAAAAaAAAAA!!! -- A Reckless Disregard for Gravity (IGF 2010 and IGC 2010 finalists; Penny Arcade PAX East Boston Indie Showcase; ModDB Editor's Choice Indie Game of the Year). Jump off buildings, create stunts, and flip people off for points!

Awesome brings you 82 remastered levels from the original, and adds 43 new ones that take place around Earth, Luna, and Ganymede.

Available now on Steam. Check us out at www.dejobaan.com/awesome.
